{
  "chapter": 51,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十一回\"奇峰迭起\"。开篇上官金虹与荆无命在晨雾中一前一后离去，暗示二人主仆关系。场景转至闹市，李寻欢带着铃铃逛街，暗中盯梢一名形迹可疑的乞丐——他怀疑此人是多年不见的朋友铁传甲。李寻欢发现另有五人也在跟踪这名乞丐，分别是卖卜瞎子（二哥）、青衣大汉、独眼妇人、瘦长江湖客（老五）和卖酒汉子，显然是一伙有组织的追杀者。众人在馄饨摊前包围了乞丐，却揭下毡帽发现是个白痴而非铁传甲——有人已用调包计救走了铁传甲。就在青衣大汉要暴打白痴时，一名白衣公子出手打断扁担，以惊人指上功力将银棍剪成碎片，震慑了这群人。瞎子识趣地带人退去。李寻欢嘱咐铃铃在小吃铺等候，独自追踪那名白痴乞丐，在僻静处与其搭话，试图打听铁传甲的下落。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "今天有雾，一定是好天气。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "今天有雾一定是好天气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我们是盯那要饭的梢么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "所以你说话一定要小声些。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他是什么人？你为什么要盯他的梢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你不懂的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就因为我不懂，所以才要问，你不告诉我，我就要大声问了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "因为他看来很像我一个多年不见的朋友。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你的朋友？难道是丐帮的门下？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "也许……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我那朋友脾气很奇怪，从不愿别人帮他的忙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢慢地跟着我们走，一个字都不要说，明白了吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "text": "你老老实实地听话，还可多活些时，若是敢乱打主意，咱们立刻就要你的命。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独眼妇人",
      "listener": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "text": "快走，还等什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独眼妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老五，这，这……是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "老五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明明是铁传甲，我一直没有放开过他，怎么会……怎么会变……变了？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是我，你是你，你为什么要打我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_jiu_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖酒汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许这厮就是铁传甲改扮的，先剥下他脸上一层皮再说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用不着，这人绝不是铁传甲。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "text": "二哥听得出他的声音？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁传甲宁死也不会被你打一巴掌不回手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_lao_wu",
      "text": "老五，你再想想，这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "老五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人一定是和铁传甲串通好了的，故意掉了包，将我们引到这里，好让那姓铁的乘机逃走。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独眼妇人",
      "listener": "char_lao_wu",
      "text": "你是干什么的？怎会让他们掉了包？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "老五",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "也许……他上厕所的时候，我总不能……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "原来你和那姓铁的是同党，我宰了你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人敢多事出手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "就是你这小子打断了我的扁担？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "text": "停住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "这位公子虽打断了你的扁担，但这锭银子要买百把根扁担也足足有余，你不多谢人家，还敢对人家无礼？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣公子",
      "listener": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "text": "好，想不到你这瞎子的眼睛竟比别的人都有用，这锭银子，就归你吧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "老朽眼睛虽瞎，心却不瞎，从不敢做昧心的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "扁担只要一钱银子一条，这锭银子却足足有十两重，公子就算要赔我们的扁担，也用不了这许多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "卖卜瞎子",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "这一钱银子老朽拜领，多下的还是物归原主！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣公子",
      "listener": "char_mai_bu_xia_zi",
      "text": "你剑法倒也不弱，只可惜太慢了些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "银子我已送出，就是你的，你还不捡起来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得威风，去得稀松，这些人至少还不愧为识时务的俊杰。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你看到那边卖包子水饺的小吃铺了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不但早就看到了，而且早就想去尝尝。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "好，你就在那里等我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你要去追那要饭的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我有话要问他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不能陪你去么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不能！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道，你又想甩开我了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我也想吃水饺，怎么会不回来？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，我就相信你，你若骗我，我就在那里等你一辈子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "朋友贵姓？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣公子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不是你的朋友，你也不是我的朋友，我不认得你，你也不认得我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_gong_zi",
      "text": "我想向你打听一个人，那人你一定认得的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    }
  ],
